00:02:21.076 --> 00:02:22.166 A:middle
Chinese even though they do

00:02:22.166 --> 00:02:23.496 A:middle
their banking in English.

00:02:25.316 --> 00:02:27.136 A:middle
In India, a student will go to

00:02:27.136 --> 00:02:29.396 A:middle
school and learn in English even

00:02:29.396 --> 00:02:30.466 A:middle
though they come home and speak

00:02:30.466 --> 00:02:31.576 A:middle
Hindi with their family.

00:02:32.906 --> 00:02:34.386 A:middle
Apps are windows into these

00:02:34.386 --> 00:02:36.476 A:middle
