00:02:58.196 --> 00:02:59.816 A:middle
application language manually in

00:02:59.816 --> 00:03:00.166 A:middle
code.

00:02:59.816 --> 00:03:00.166 A:middle
code.

00:03:00.916 --> 00:03:02.806 A:middle
