00:03:02.806 --> 00:03:04.036 A:middle
ensure users get the right

00:03:04.036 --> 00:03:05.526 A:middle
language and font fall backs.

00:03:06.626 --> 00:03:07.956 A:middle
If you do need to add the option

00:03:07.956 --> 00:03:08.966 A:middle
within your app to switch

00:03:08.966 --> 00:03:10.666 A:middle
languages, we recommend you

00:03:10.666 --> 00:03:12.126 A:middle
Launch into Settings where users

00:03:12.126 --> 00:03:13.216 A:middle
can go in and switch the

00:03:13.216 --> 00:03:14.766 A:middle
language of your app.

00:03:15.696 --> 00:03:18.386 A:middle
