So please check out the Testing

00:22:00.576 --> 00:22:01.866 A:middle
in Xcode session on Thursday

00:22:01.866 --> 00:22:04.136 A:middle
morning to learn more about it.

00:22:04.956 --> 00:22:06.616 A:middle
What we will be covering is how

00:22:06.666 --> 00:22:08.726 A:middle
you can use test plans in your

00:22:08.726 --> 00:22:10.546 A:middle
localization workflow.

00:22:11.896 --> 00:22:14.526 A:middle
So, first, we will see how you

00:22:14.526 --> 00:22:15.616 A:middle
can make sure that your test

00:22:15.616 --> 00:22:18.916 A:middle
localization friendly, then

00:22:19.406 --> 00:22:20.466 A:middle
we'll talk about how you can use

00:22:20.506 --> 00:22:22.466 A:middle
test plans to generate localized

00:22:23.196 --> 00:22:23.476 A:middle
